window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When linguist Andrew Dennison is yanked from his bed by the Secret Service and taken to a top secret facility in the desert, he has no idea he's been brought there to translate the words of an ancient demon. </p> <p>He joins pretty but cold veterinarian Sun Jones, eccentric molecular biologist Dr. Frank Belgium, and a hodge-podge of religious, military, and science personnel to try and figure out if the creature is, indeed, Satan. </p> <p>But things quickly go bad, and very soon Andy isn't just fighting for his life, but the lives of everyone on earthâ€¦ </p>"; 
